00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,000
 I'm sorry about that.

155
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:36,000
 No.

156
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,000
 I have a lot more at home.

157
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,000
 Would you like to come and see it next time?

158
